description.en:
Whadda spare parts kit for raspberry pi

Gender: unisex
Material: plastic, steel, copper
Dimensions storage box: 18,6 x 9 x 4,5 cm (L x W x H)

Contents:
1 Solderless breadboard, 830 insertion points
10 10K resistor (RA10K0)
10 560R resistor (RA560E0)
1 1602 LCD module (LCD1602BLC)

1 T-shaped GPIO expansion board
1 Flat cable for GPIO board
1 IR receiver (WPI317)
1 Mini remote control for WPI317
1 DS18B20 digital temperature sensor (1 wire)
1 50K potentiometer (K047AM)

2 Green LED 5 mm
1 RGB LED 5 mm
1 40-pin male pin header (2.54 mm), single row
1 Cable with 3-pin female connector - 20 cm

1 Transparent storage box
